        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>America's Revegetation and Carbon Sequestration Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill addresses climate change through efforts to sequester, mitigate, or store carbon dioxide, such as salvage logging, revegetation, or reforestation efforts, on National Forest System land and other land as specified by the bill.</p>]]>
        </text>
